          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "An HSIIDC allottee files periodic project implementation and production status returns on the HSIIDC portal, pays annual ground rent or lease charges by the due date, and keeps its Haryana Enterprises Promotion Portal registration and Consent to Operate current. Missing a project implementation deadline triggers extension fees, and prolonged non-implementation can lead to resumption of the plot."
          }
